<% layout('layouts/boilerplate') %>
<div class="container mt-3 mb-5">
    <h1 class="text-center mb-4">About Us</h1>

    <section class="mb-5">
        <h2 class="h4 text-primary mb-3">Our Mission</h2>
        <p>
            Boomerang was built to launch ideas into reality by empowering
            creators worldwide through innovative platforms and community.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-5">
        <h2 class="h4 text-primary mb-3">Our Platform</h2>
        <p>
            Boomerang is where ideas find their wings. It's a place where
            creators share their inspirations, and communities unite to make
            them a reality. From the spark of an idea to its shining moment,
            Boomerang connects you directly with those who share your passion.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-5">
        <h2 class="h4 text-primary mb-3">Our Community</h2>
        <p>
            It all begins with you. Your spark ignites a movement. Friends
            become supporters, and supporters become champions. Together, we
            create a ripple effect. Our community unites creators and backers
            alike, bound by a shared love for innovation and artistry.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-5">
        <h2 class="h4 text-primary mb-3">Our Values</h2>
        <p>
            Your vision. Your voice. No compromises. No exhaustive grant
            applications. No demands to alter your message. At Boomerang, you
            hold the reins of your creation. Backers join you on your journey,
            becoming part of something extraordinary.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-5">
        <h2 class="h4 text-primary mb-3">Our Commitment</h2>
        <p>
            We're dedicated to cultivating a space where creativity thrives. By
            removing barriers and empowering creators, we democratize the
            artistic process. We prioritize meaningful impact over all else,
            ensuring our actions reflect our core values.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-5">
        <h2 class="h4 text-primary mb-3">Our Team</h2>
        <p>
            We're a collective of dreamers and doers—designers, developers,
            artists, and athletes—all passionate about supporting the creative
            ecosystem. We've navigated the path of bringing ideas to life, and
            we're here to help you every step of the way.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2 class="h4 text-primary mb-3">Our Journey Has Just Begun...</h2>
        <p>
            Join us as we continue to empower creators and communities around
            the world.
        </p>
    </section>
</div>
